3704b37e5336"],

Cell["\<\
Additional input to version 2.5, 2.6 and 2.7 by Jyrki Rantaharju. 
Additional input to version 2.6 by Andreas Brinkmann. 
Isotope property tables in version 2.6.1 by Soumya Singha Roy. 
Modifications leading to v2.12 programmed by Malcolm Levitt and stimulated by \
Phil Kuchel, Jean-Nicolas Dumez, Russ Bowers and Andreas Brinkmann.
Additional input to version 3.0.0 by Christian Bengs. 
Additional input, revision of older routines and new features added to \
version 3.1.0 and later by Malcolm Levitt and Christian Bengs. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5443603310244517`*^9, 3.5443604202146378`*^9}, {
   3.544364079831048*^9, 3.544364109248547*^9}, {3.545670638036495*^9, 
