Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Limitations", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.544413113452461*^9, 3.544413117891059*^9}, {
  3.54441324522621*^9, 
  3.544413246823179*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e5ec0139-ec8f-4ec3-9739-\
0816bea1ecea"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Although ",
 StyleBox["SpinDynamica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " is very versatile, it is not suitable for every calculation in magnetic \
resonance. Some of the known limitations (in v3.9) are as follows:\n\t* ",
 StyleBox["spin system size: ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "The ",
 StyleBox["SpinDynamica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " code is general for any spin system, but the current code becomes slow and \
very memory intensive beyond about 6 coupled spins. It is planned to \
incorporate custom codes such as reduced Liouville spaces in the future, to \
allow approximate simulations of larger spin systems.\n\t* ",
 StyleBox["chemical exchange. ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 StyleBox["SpinDynamica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " allows arbitrary relaxation mechanisms in the Redfield regime (short \
correlation time compared to the size of the fluctuating interaction). Slower \
fluctuating interactions, such as chemical exchange problems, are not yet \
handled explicitly (although they may be simulated by performing ensemble \
averages of time-domain calculations). It is expected that chemical exchange \
will be included in the near future. \n\t* ",
 StyleBox["multidimensional spectroscopy. ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "At this point, there is no specific code for generating multidimensional \
NMR signals in a computationally-efficient way. \n\tI hope very much that the \
user community will help address some of these restrictions by contributing \
their own add-on packages. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.544412577743538*^9, 3.544412651790648*^9}, {
   3.544412689828652*^9, 3.54441298767888*^9}, {3.544413027569848*^9, 
   3.544413089740077*^9}, 3.545042873752466*^9, 3.5726310860366697`*^9, 
   3.583347038348752*^9, {3.588071204690116*^9, 3.588071205804823*^9}, 
   3.590671097949985*^9, {3.6058079465588703`*^9, 3.605807947225777*^9}, 
   3.614926451009289*^9, {3.616743525139189*^9, 3.616743525270844*^9}, {
   3.61674355865414*^9, 3.616743560833917*^9}, 3.626943879955768*^9, {
   3.630585206825624*^9, 3.630585207012253*^9}, 3.640873045349886*^9, {
   3.916897235626094*^9, 
   3.916897245929471*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b2984a58-6f2f-46ad-8280-\
ed1d202de949"]
}, Open  ]],

