Cell["\<\
The messages above indicate the spin system has been set and also that a \
basis for the operator calculations has been set up. You may ignore the \
BasisLabels setting, for now.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.544369963127462*^9, 3.544369988845619*^9}, {
  3.616744214439595*^9, 
