This syntax is used to specify the J-coupling Hamiltonian between a pair of \
spins.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.544371205846347*^9, 
  3.54437122474776*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"27c426c3-1383-4c0c-995f-\
ce2a240cfd97"]
