Cell["\<\
This generates a product of superoperators which is equivalent to the \
requested rotation. The syntax above generates a rotation by 90\[Degree] \
about an axis in the xy plane, rotated away from the x-axis towards the \
y-axis by 45\[Degree].\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.54437970250953*^9, 3.544379716477082*^9}, {
  3.544413423568154*^9, 
  3.544413468496546*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5514115e-c454-4030-8376-\
376f38f17687"],

Cell["\<\
The rotation angle and axis may also be specified using polar angles, as \
follows:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.544379724911016*^9, 
  3.544379737614528*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2af1679f-e947-4b42-b329-\
288341e0239a"],

